{"word":"G3114 - μακροθυμέω - makrothyméō - mak-roth-oo-meh'-o - Bear long","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μακροθυμέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">makrothyméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mak-roth-oo-meh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bear long</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொறுமையாயிரு, சாந்தமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to persevere patiently and bravely"},{"paragraph":"2. to be patient"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G3116 - μακροθυμώς - makrothymṓs - mak-roth-oo-moce'/3116\">G3116</a>; to <i>be long spirited</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>forbearing</i> or (subjectively) <i>patient:</i> - bear (suffer) long, be longsuffering, have (long) patience, be patient, patiently endure.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3114/3114\">G3114</a>, <a href=\"#/G3115/3115\">G3115</a>, <a href=\"#/G3116/3116\">G3116</a>"}]}